summary:
I have extensive equine experience as I have worked with many others restaurant in my country. Through working with restaurant, I have acquired a thorough knowledge of cleaning and maintening hygiene.

While I have equine experience, I also have excellent communication skills and an aptitude for customer service. My experience as a volunteer at chillox (A Bangladeshi company) made it necessary for me to focus on providing quality customer service, and also enabled me to work with all types of people. I believe that my communication skills, partnered with my equine knowledge, would make me an asset to your company.

Thank you for your consideration. I can be reached at +31684796797 or himu962@gmail.com. I look forward to hearing from you soon.
